item.title: My 2010
item.description: All in all not a bad year, I would say. Just a quick overview of some highlights and the soundtrack of the last year. The Good Engaged to Nelleke Bachelor of Science Started a business Royal Haskoning Rock Climbing! / Spain Trip the Harry Potter Septology Spotify! Water Insight Android Vienna Pablo Picasso’s violin Mac Mini Beatles Discography Reading, reading reading. Met awesome people. Etc.
